## Troubleshooting

| Problem | Fix |
|---|---|
| `openssl-sys` build error | `apt install pkg-config libssl-dev` (Ubuntu) / `brew install openssl` (macOS) |
| Tests fail after adding SQLite column | Run against a fresh `TempDir` — tests never share state |
| `database is locked` | Only one writer at a time; check for stale processes |

Lemonade-specific troubleshooting lives in `environment-config.mdc`.
